  </p>
  <p>
  梦想用 ai 打造跟我一摸一样的数字人，这样我只用专注享受生活
  </p>
  <p>My motto: Everything is Just for fun <Spoiler>life is a movie</Spoiler></p>
  <Button title='Sponsor Me' class='w-fit' href='/projects#sponsorship' style='ahead' />

  {/* general-talk */}
